{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was painting the pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You had to know how to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you had to-- it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Believe me, we worked 12 hours a day, 7 days a week, and it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But for-- from work, we were not afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We tried to do the best job, in order to satisfy Schindler and satisfy his requirement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Department.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was we were drawing shells for the guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody said it was for V-2, for the missiles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody said for guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't know exactly, but we-- there was an item which was needed to fight the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- many times, he was away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the time he was in the office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But just to see him-- to see him walking around made us to feel better, you know, somebody who cares, somebody who is-- and he didn't spoke to us, didn't ever spoke to us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just gave you a nice look was enough, too, that he's around, and we felt better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Along with this, he was also bribing the guards, the SS people around, that they wouldn't harass us after the work, because actually, after the working hours, we belonged to the SS people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't belong to the-- to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he did everything possible to make conditions a little bearable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I could say that he was a remarkable man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We owed him a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't-- there was no guarantee that we were going to survive the war, even with Schindler, because once we were ordered to go back to Plaszow, when we start liquidating his factory, there was no guarantee at all.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were again under the Nazis' SS rules.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Amon Goeth was in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
